    intro: "Shivampet is the mandal headquarters of Shivampet mandal in Medak district, with a mandal population of 45,132 (Census 2011) spread over 199 km² across 27 villages. The mandal falls under HMDA Master Plan 2031 coverage. This page layers the Master Plan as an interactive overlay on satellite imagery, enabling you to search a survey number or landmark and toggle the zoning view to verify the land-use designation and reserved areas.",
    paragraphs: ["Shivampet mandal falls under Narsapur Assembly Constituency and Medak Parliamentary Constituency. It hosts numerous water bodies, indicating its position in the HMDA periphery zone.","Use the map to search your survey number or nearby landmark, then toggle the Master Plan overlay to confirm zoning and reserved land use. The plan horizon extends to 2031 and marks areas designated for public infrastructure, green belts and transportation corridors."],
