    intro: "Vita is the taluka headquarters of Khanapur (Vita) taluka and a municipal council in Sangli district. Located in a region known for sugarcane cultivation and associated agro-industries, Vita has earned recognition for urban infrastructure and sanitation initiatives, ranking top in cleanliness in its population category at the 2021 Swachh Survekshan Awards. This page opens the Development Plan layer covering Vita as an interactive overlay on satellite imagery, enabling you to read the land-use zone, reservations and road lines for any plot.",
